the subconscious now conscious.

00:08:58.920 --> 00:09:02.720 align:middle line:84%
You're unfolding the full
potential of the human being.

00:09:02.720 --> 00:09:07.280 align:middle line:84%
You're cleaning the machine
of stresses, anxieties,

00:09:07.280 --> 00:09:12.400 align:middle line:84%
depression, hate,
anger, rage, despair,

00:09:12.400 --> 00:09:16.865 align:middle line:84%
and fear so you live and work
in more and more freedom.

00:09:16.865 --> 00:09:20.600 align:middle line:90%


