and those things that
used to stress you

00:09:29.910 --> 00:09:34.550 align:middle line:84%
don't have the
same power anymore.

00:09:34.550 --> 00:09:36.880 align:middle line:90%
This is magical.

00:09:36.880 --> 00:09:39.790 align:middle line:90%
How beautiful is this?

00:09:39.790 --> 00:09:41.530 align:middle line:90%
How beautiful is this?

00:09:41.530 --> 00:09:44.470 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:09:44.470 --> 00:10:02.640 align:middle line:90%


00:10:02.640 --> 00:10:09.860 align:middle line:84%
The sunlight in LA
makes me feel freedom.

00:10:09.860 --> 00:10:15.290 align:middle line:84%
And it makes me feel the
field of all possibilities.

00:10:15.290 --> 00:10:18.560 align:middle line:90%


00:10:18.560 --> 00:10:21.480 align:middle line:84%
And that's a nice
thing to think about.

00:10:21.480 --> 00:10:25.860 align:middle line:84%
Maharishi said, "Don't
fight the darkness.

00:10:25.860 --> 00:10:28.590 align:middle line:90%
Don't even worry about it.

00:10:28.590 --> 00:10:31.260 align:middle line:90%
Simply turn on the light."

00:10:31.260 --> 00:10:34.400 align:middle line:90%


00:10:34.400 --> 00:10:38.480 align:middle line:84%
Get down in there, and
darkness, negativity

00:10:38.480 --> 00:10:44.060 align:middle line:90%
goes away in time for sure.

00:10:44.060 --> 00:10:47.110 align:middle line:90%
